\[
E'=\frac{1}{2}m\left(v_{0}^{2}+\left(\frac{I}{m}\right)^{2}\right)+\frac{1}{2}kr_{0}^{2}=\underbrace{\frac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}+\frac{1}{2}kr_{0}^{2}}_{=E}+\frac{1}{2}m\left(\frac{I}{m}\right)^{2}=
\]

