\end_inset

.
 Reordenando términos y usando 
\begin_inset Formula ${\displaystyle \frac{\partial V}{\partial r}\left(r\right)=-F\left(r\right)}$
\end_inset

, llegamos a:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m\dot{r}\ddot{r}-\frac{L^{2}}{mr^{3}}\dot{r}-F\left(r\right)\dot{r}=0
\]

\end_inset

Dividiendo por 
\begin_inset Formula $m\dot{r}$
\end_inset

, obtenemos:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ddot{r}-\frac{L^{2}}{m^{2}r^{3}}-\frac{F\left(r\right)}{m}=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

